Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情本王都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於貴國所發生的災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣身為人民的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王對您感到同情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您,弗雷特公王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:02:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也已經知曉寨巴哈的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此本王也才會緊急趕回都城戈達西姆來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論理由為何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士棄國即為不義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違背君命即為不忠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為弗雷特會需要這種 不忠不義之輩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連他們是為了我們國家,才會如此不顧性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還看穿幻人的偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊退了寨巴哈的偵查員…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住□!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要進言再等個十年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會因為你的獨斷,而讓這個國家步上滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,有話待會兒再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我的無禮,姊夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我現在已經沒有資格,這樣喊您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也捨棄了自己的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王殿下,寨巴哈的侵略已近乎瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎打算將整個蓋亞,捲入戰亂的漩渦中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇絕不會僅發生於法尼利亞一國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的下一個攻打目標即為弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很遺憾地,父王他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,阿斯頓王打算對此放任不理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他認為那麼做才是真正為阿斯多利亞好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當整個蓋亞都落入了寨巴哈手中之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞真的可能獨自享有和平嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾為了阻止此事發生因此隻身來到弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王殿下,請您原諒亞連吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既聰明且仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞有位好公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你願意成為我國兵士與寨巴哈對抗嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下性命已交付公王之手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王相當期待你的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是西特的父親?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月的少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那名少女能夠輕易看出 身披隱形披風的人型裝甲位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說還能透過預測命運將龍引導至有利位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想見識那股能夠影響 我的命運預測裝置的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠回憶的彼方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷□開始在癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不在乎阿斯多利亞,還有弗雷特會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你能平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,小瞳有沒有來這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,她沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我還是會看到呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也還真不膩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不瞭解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了,為什麼我還是會看到呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦,為什麼?為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩死人了,梵大人在找你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,簡直是傷痕纍纍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王你用劍太粗魯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝拉撒特的劍,連半條傷痕也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不像亞連那麼會用劍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王在鬧脾氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長他當然也會把劍弄傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒你厲害就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能借用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,我不是要你一同上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠說中未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠發現隱形的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望你能用那股力量 告訴我寨巴哈會從哪裏攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此,這點子不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是順利的話,就能給他們來個下馬威
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就是我們的勝利女神囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我想得那麼好用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在地球上,只是個普通的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜也只是稍微比其他人準確一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…在來到蓋亞之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜居然準得讓我感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還常常看到一些恐怖的預見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再依靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再叫我占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再讓我看到恐怖的預見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳幫我算算我和我男朋友的速配程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,是我先的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候跟他告白比較好,幫我算算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳算得好準喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜明明只能算是一種遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了,無論是占卜還是預見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪蓮妮生前住過的離宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將她在嫁過來之前 使用過的建築物整個搬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都還是跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還維持原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就隨你自由使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做我相信,瑪蓮妮一定也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要離開了是嗎,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪蓮妮公主,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊,祝您幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡不著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得要是現在睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就沒辦法再醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我想睡覺時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦裏就會浮現出戰爭的事,讓我不停地發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…就如同父王所說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不具備成為王者的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再依靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法變得像父王一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后也是希望我能成為了不起的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總是說亞連的事跡給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法達成母后及父王的期許
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說都具有不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾聽我祖母說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能變成那樣 自己要是能那樣該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心裏一直想著這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來夢想就一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想會實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一直想著要變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就會好好努力,好好加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,相反地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老覺得行不通 老想著自己絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的夢想不可能會實現的話 那就真的會沒辦法成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要強烈地抱持希望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天,夢想就會傳達到那顆星星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而星星就會助我們 最後的一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星會幫助我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子,我來幫你算算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來替你問問星星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔羅牌占卜就是借助星星的力量來占卜未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來算算你的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃三十四之月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾葉巴王叔帶我,一起去參觀武術大會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該是擔心我 老是待在房間裏才這麼做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我對武術明明就毫無興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞騎士團的年輕天才劍客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是瑪蓮妮王姊的日記?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧十二之月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮青年被任命為"天空騎士"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:16:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞王國中僅十二位 備受載譽的騎士才得以乘其名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是當之無愧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接下了王宮的警備工作而來到帕拉斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對父王撒的嬌,看來是生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L'lmperatore（皇帝）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Giustizia（正義）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後你會慢慢累積實力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得大家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LA Luota（命運之輪）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將會通過某個重大考驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤三之月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與弗雷特公王的婚約已成定局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會生於王家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經愛上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是生於王家的女子與騎士的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,我明明就如此深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪蓮妮王姊對亞連…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的,是那晚的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴公王的話,他會說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會扳起手指頭細數…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是不可能瞞得了他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神好像沒辦法集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顛倒的LA lmperatrce（女帝）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁忌之戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說西特是亞連跟瑪蓮妮王姊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈四魔軍好久沒全員到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,亞德羅福斯將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您能夠成為這次戰爭的先鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦陣形排列完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願神明給予庇護!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍出征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青銅軍,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑鐵軍,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白銀軍,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有那麼多人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王,敵軍似乎已於四方佈陣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數約有五萬五千人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型裝甲超過一萬架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想死守城門…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯,你應該很清楚 我們生為弗雷特人的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來執行傳承之書"獅子之卷"的日子到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳承之書"獅子之卷"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到城門去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,小瞳就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,請您一定要平安歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,你們駕駛庫魯傑特飛到城的上方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要駕駛謝拉撒特迎敵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,我想問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和瑪蓮妮公主有關,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實曾與瑪蓮妮公主相愛過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她與弗雷特公王的婚姻成定局前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,西特王子很可能是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍擊隊已就定位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時維持原狀待命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦攻入城後按照計劃行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,軍師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家犧牲生命為的只是要讓我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血紅的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:57.19,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:05.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:13.27,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:19.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:21.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:26.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.63,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:34.43,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:49.41,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:57.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:13.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:19.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
